description:
In this unedited holiday bonus, Danny counts down his favorite Bravo reality episodes of 2018. He talks about all the iconic moments from #RHONY and the rest of the Housewives, Flipping Out, Married to Medicine, Shahs, Southern Charm, Below Deck, and more!


*To support this podcast and for bonus episodes, visit Patreon.com/EverythingIconic
